Appendix G: Notation and Assumptions Summary

Symbol Meaning
\mathcal{S},\mathcal{A},\mathcal{O} State, action, observation spaces
T, \Omega Transition and observation kernels
R, d Cost and constraint cost functions
\gamma Discount factor
z Latent state
q_\phi Encoder distribution
